PROJECT - 2
NOTE:

Create your own account in the website http://a.testaddressbook.com/sign_in
manually before you start your automation. I suggest you to use a fake email address.
This is just for testing.

STEPS:
1. Navigate to http://a.testaddressbook.com/sign_in
2. Enter the username and password
3. Click on sign in button
4. Click on Addresses
5. Click on new address button
6. Enter the first name "Fernando"
7. Enter the last name "Torres"
8. Enter the address 1 "Anfield Rd"
9. Enter the address 2 "Anfield"
10. Enter the city "Liverpool"
11. Choose a RANDOM option from the state dropdown
12. Enter the Zipcode "L4 0TH"
13. Click on United States
14. Enter the birthday "20/03/1984"
15. Enter the age "36"
16. Enter the WebSite "https://www.google.com/"
17. Enter the phone "8625747878"
18. Click on Climbing and Dancing
19. Enter the Note "Never Back Down"
20. Click on Create Address button
21. Verify if the first name is "Fernando"
22. Verify if the last name is "Torres"
23. Click on Addresses
24. Click on Edit button
25. Change the first name as "Peter"
26. Change the last name as "Crouch"
27. Click on Update address
28. Verify if the first name is "Peter"
29. Verify if the last name is "Crouch"
30. Click on Addresses
31. Click on Destroy
32. Confirm deleting the address
33. Verify if the address was removed
34. Quit the browser